{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"032d71d4a0","title":"为日本工人朋友们题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6519a1e5e3","index":0,"year":1962,"month":9,"day":18,"articleId":"032d71d4a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"ac5b0cfafd","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东1962年9月18日接见了由日本工人教育协会副会长官川实率领的日本工人学习积极分子代表团，和他们进行了亲切友好的谈话，并且为日本工人朋友们写了这个题词。当时对题词没有报道。1968年，在这个题词六周年之际，《人民日报》用第一版一整版的篇幅，报道了这个题词，刊载了题词手迹。"}],"contents":[{"id":"99c24b352c","type":"title","text":"为日本工人朋友们题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0"},{"id":"ac5b0cfafd","type":"paragraph","text":"只要认真做到马克思列宁主义的普遍真理与日本革命的具体实践相结合，日本革命的胜利就是毫无疑义的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0"},{"id":"c5ebde056b","type":"paragraph","text":"应日本工人学习积极分子访华代表团各位朋友之命，书赠日本工人朋友们。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0"},{"id":"a1c0f1c19f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0"},{"id":"f1cd19f8f6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年九月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0"}],"page":{"id":"863b8921ab","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"032d71d4a0","start":249,"end":249}}}},"__N_SSG":true}